{"tid":1094884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人執到張 1189737 嘅八達通","createTime":"2019-04-06T15:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T08:07:15.000Z","uid":200663,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27f5848bdb81bfe3766484ba1f559a1d74b328d6","tid":1094884,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日搭三點九班 290X 由荃灣返屋企<br />\n喺葵俊苑落車嗰陣跌咗張八達通 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3rmRgjb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3rmRgjb.png&h=dbabae90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張八達通跟埋九巴月票買 張卡右下角寫住 1017 㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張八達通我用嚟買月票 點知買咗一個星期就唔見咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連埋政府個交通費回水即係張卡值成九百幾蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九百幾蚊可能對執到嘅人嚟講濕濕碎<br />\n但呢到已經係我返 pt 半個月糧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且執到據為己有 係就係坐車唔使比錢<br />\n但你用一個唔識嘅人啲錢都會內疚啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果執到嘅話 請你交去警署啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經去咗報失喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多請返你食飯啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 一落車已經同咗九巴報失 但站長話搵唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4fa87acf860194e72ec0dfb3b2d7403975ce40","tid":1094884,"uid":222127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"希望你快d搵得番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecad8956415846b8be19746a3b8dc324e0d12ef","tid":1094884,"uid":240918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"返partime半個月糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ab1e